metadata.name: Aston Martin DB5
metadata.description:
Aston Martin DB5 

The iconic Aston Martin DB5 was released in 1963. It is a luxury grand tourer made by British luxury sports cars manufacturer Aston Martin.

 It was a slight upgrade from the DB4 which preceded it.

The DB5 is most famous for being the third, but most recognized, James Bond car.

It's designed by Carrozzeria Touring Superleggera. It has DOHC Straight-6, 4.0 L (3,995 cc) 282â€“325 bhp engine.

In this NFT, you can recognize the image of a powerful woman in the background. You can see iconic symbol 007 in her wavy hair.
